Welcome to Math Quest for Kids! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle user data when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information from users. Math Quest for Kids is a standalone game that does not require account creation, personal data submission, or any form of tracking.

2. How We Use Information

Since we do not collect any user data, there is no information to use, share, or process.

3. Third-Party Services

Our app does not integrate with any third-party services that collect personal data. If we include ads or analytics in future updates, we will update this Privacy Policy accordingly.

4. Data Security

As we do not collect or store any user data, there is no risk of unauthorized access or misuse of personal information.

5. Children's Privacy

Math Quest for Kids is designed for children and complies with privacy regulations such as COPPA. Since no data is collected, there is no risk of exposure to personal information.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected within the app or on our official website.

